# Project: OWONA WhatsApp Platform

## Tech Stack

- Next.js 15 App Router
- Supabase Auth (PKCE Flow)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- PM2 Deployment
- Multilingual: /[locale]/ routing

## Key Patterns

- Client-side Supabase: createBrowserClient()
- Server-side: createServerClient()
- Auth pages: app/[locale]/auth/*
- RLS active on all tables

## Common Issues

- PKCE codes consumed by email link scanners
- Apple Mail preview triggers auth links
- Need explicit user interaction before exchangeCodeForSession()

## Coding Style

- Use TypeScript strict mode
- Prefer server components, mark 'use client' explicitly
- Error handling with try-catch and user-friendly messages
- Toast notifications for user feedback

